      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in impeccable, showroom-quality condition, truly a rare find for the meticulous collector. The exterior paint is absolutely flawless, maintaining a deep, factory-fresh luster without a single swirl mark or chip. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with every surface looking and feeling brand new, and all electronic features functioning perfectly. This car has been stored in a climate-controlled environment and has seen very limited, careful use, making it as close to a new vehicle as you can find on the market.",
